{
  "stem": "13313.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were all kind of rumors as to what happened to those people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There were always rumors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "People being optimistic by nature always hoped for the best, and ignore rumors that are bad news.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my Mother-- also they started to go to houses, because now they had this list of people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we heard that so-and-so had been picked up, and so-and-so had been picked up, and not necessarily restricted to the typically Jewish center.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my mother then started to have us stay with Gentile friends that knew us from our business and stay a few days here, a few days there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were afraid to stay in our own home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we basically not return home other than once in a while to pick something up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We stayed with Gentile people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and the rumors were such, that it was dangerous to stay with children, so my mother decided she had to do something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had to organize ourselves to go into permanent hiding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From [INAUDIBLE] we picked up and deported god knows where.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was a very smart and courageous lady, and she thought on her feet, literally.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had-- when we had this beauty salon, we knew a couple of-- a Christian couple that were actually ran a placement service, like a personnel service.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they always supplied us-- whenever we needed someone in the salon, male or female, hairdressers or barbers, or haircutters, we-- they used to supply us with those people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we knew them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had no children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were already-- it's hard for me, thinking back to judge how old they are, because when you're nine years old everybody over 30 looks old.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I think they must have been, in my opinion, in their mid '40s.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
